{"id": "1340295612494647358", "channel_id": "1339473678819266561", "type": 19, "author_id": "885882671899746305", "author_name": "_cwz_", "author_bot": false, "content": "其實我覺得不至於到整個星辰篇都不好啦（雖然我投否\n你這標題有點太片面\n認真說真心話的話\n我最討厭的就是把黑潮的狂氣上限提升常駐，還有密契可能要重刷這一點", "timestamp": "2025-02-15T12:16:15.507000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-02-15T12:16:39.440000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["594196021119287316"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1340294727362154496", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1339473678819266561", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：V2.1.0.2 星辰篇规则", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
